metadata.name: O X
metadata.description:
The theme of house on head was something that I made back in 2019 and perhaps the theme that I enjoyed doing the most. My first mint on Foundation was also depicting a house on head, hence, it is only wise to continue the series and make a collection of it. O X is the first in the collection and the fifth I have made, with many more to come.

The owner will also received a still image in .png format of the NFT.

Video format (.mp4 || 2400 x 2700 pixels)
